From 56294fc32f902eee10d758e653454aec8bd9d5c3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Jul 2026 15:34:20 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Hide the Gecko surface owner

Firefox kept a window to keep pixels in flight,
Now alpha is zero and focus stays light.
Resize epochs cross without AX in the hall,
While WebRender keeps painting tiles through it all.
---
 .../AstrohackerVisibleWindow.sys.mjs          | 164 +++++++++++++++++-
 gfx/layers/AstrohackerSurfaceExporterMac.mm   |   7 +-
 widget/cocoa/nsCocoaWindow.mm                 |  95 +++++++++-
 3 files changed, 258 insertions(+), 8 deletions(-)

